167 int acwing4204::main(istream &cin, ostream &cout) {
168 int n;
169 const int N = 1010;
170 auto *g = new int *[N];
171 for(int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
172 g[i] = new int[N];
173 for(int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
174 g[i][j] = 0;
175 }
176 }
177 cin >> n;
178 for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
179 g[1][i] = i - 1;
180 g[i][1] = i - 1;
181 }
182 for(int i = 2; i < n; i++) {
183 for(int j = 2; j < n; j++) {
184 if(i == j) {
185 g[i][j] = 0;//对角线为0
186 } else {
187 if(g[i][j - 1] == 0) {
188 //在0后面一格
189 g[i][j] = g[i - 1][j] + 1;//上面一格的值+1
190 } else {
191 //否则
192 g[i][j] = g[i][j - 1] + 1;//前面一格的值+1
193 }
194 if(g[i][j] == n) {
195 //达到上限
196 g[i][j] = 1;//回归到1
197 }
198 }
199 }
200 }
201 for(int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
202 set<int> s;
203 for(int j = 1; j < n; j++) {
204 s.insert(g[i][j]);
205 }
206 for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
207 if(!s.contains(j)) {
208 g[i][n] = g[n][i] = j;//补最后一列和最后一行的值
209 }
210 }
211 }
212
213 //输出
214 for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
215 for(int j = 1; j <= n; j++) {
216 cout << g[i][j];
217 if(j != n) {
218 cout << " ";
219 }
220 }
221 if(i != n) {
222 cout << endl;
223 }
224 }
225 for(int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
226 delete[] g[i];
227 }
228 delete[] g;
229 return 0;
230 }

317 char cowhide[55][55]{};
318 bool occupy[55][55]{};
319 auto edge = unordered_set<point, pointhash, pointequal>();
320 int n;
321 int m;
322 cin >> n >> m;
323 bool flag = true;
324 point first{};
325 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
326 for(int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
327 cin >> cowhide[i][j];
328 if(flag && cowhide[i][j] == 'X') {
329 occupy[i][j] = true;
330 first = point(i, j);
331 flag = false;
332 } else {
333 occupy[i][j] = false;
334 }
335 }
336 }
337
338 flood(first, occupy, &edge, cowhide, n, m);
339
340 int count = 0;
341 auto nextedge = unordered_set<point, pointhash, pointequal>();
342 while(true) {
343 for(const auto p: edge) {
344 point nexts[] = {
345 point(p.x + 1, p.y), point(p.x - 1, p.y), point(p.x, p.y + 1),
346 point(p.x, p.y - 1)};
347 for(auto next: nexts) {
348 if(0 <= next.x && next.x <= n && 0 <= next.y && next.y <= m && !occupy[next.x][next.y]) {
349 if(cowhide[next.x][next.y] == 'X') {
350 cout << count;
351 return 0;
352 }
353 cowhide[next.x][next.y] = 'X';
354 occupy[next.x][next.y] = true;
355 nextedge.insert(next);
356 }
357 }
358 }
359 count++;
360 edge = nextedge;
361 nextedge = unordered_set<point, pointhash, pointequal>();
362 }

364
365 size_t pointhash::operator()(const point &p) const { return p.x * 50 + p.y; }
366
367 bool pointequal::operator()(const point &p1, const point &p2) const { return p1.x == p2.x && p1.y == p2.y; }
368
369 void
370 flood(point first, bool occupy[55][55], unordered_set<point, pointhash, pointequal> *edge, char cowhide[55][55],
371 int n, int m) {
372 auto que = queue<point>();
373 const auto eq = pointequal();
374 que.push(first);
375 while(!que.empty()) {
376 auto p = que.front();
377 if(!eq(p, first) && occupy[p.x][p.y]) {
378 que.pop();
379 continue;
380 }
381 occupy[p.x][p.y] = true;
382 point nexts[] = {point(p.x + 1, p.y), point(p.x - 1, p.y), point(p.x, p.y + 1), point(p.x, p.y - 1)};
383 for(auto next: nexts) {
384 if(0 <= next.x && next.x <= n && 0 <= next.y && next.y <= m && !occupy[next.x][next.y]) {
385 if(cowhide[next.x][next.y] == 'X') {
386 que.push(next);
387 } else {
388 edge->insert(p);
389 }
390 }
391 }
392 que.pop();
393 }
394 }

432
433 int bfs(point start, int **field, int max_x, int max_y) {
434 auto que = deque<point>();
435 que.push_front(start);
436 while(!que.empty()) {
437 const auto p = que.front();
438 que.pop_front();
439 point nexts[] = {
440 point(p.x + 1, p.y, p.step), point(p.x - 1, p.y, p.step),
441 point(p.x, p.y + 1, p.step), point(p.x, p.y - 1, p.step)};
442 for(auto next: nexts) {
443 if(next.x == 0 && next.y == 0) {
444 return next.step;
445 }
446 if(0 <= next.x && next.x <= max_x + 2 && 0 <= next.y && next.y <= max_y + 2 &&
447 field[next.x][next.y] != 2) {
448 if(field[next.x][next.y] == 0) {
449 que.push_front(next);
450 } else {
451 //field[nexts.first][nexts.second]==1
452 next.step++;
453 que.push_back(next);
454 }
455 field[next.x][next.y] = 2;
456 }
457 }
458 }
459 return start.step;
460 }

582 int acwing2005::dfs(bool stage, char horseshoes[5][5], const bool picked[5][5], int count, int level, int x, int y,
583 int n) {
584 if(level == 0 && !stage) {
585 if(count == 13) {
586 printf("13");
587 }
588 return count;
589 }
590
591 pair<int, int> nexts[4] = {pair(x - 1, y), pair(x + 1, y), pair(x, y - 1),
592 pair(x, y + 1)};
593 //复制状态
594 bool picked_cpy[5][5];
595 memcpy(picked_cpy, picked, sizeof picked_cpy);
596
597 int max = 0;
598 picked_cpy[x][y] = true;
599
600 for(const auto next: nexts) {
601 if(0 <= next.first && next.first < n && 0 <= next.second && next.second < n &&
602 !picked_cpy[next.first][next.second]) {
603 int res = 0;
604 if(stage && horseshoes[next.first][next.second] == '(') {
605 res = dfs(true, horseshoes, picked_cpy, count + 1, level + 1, next.first, next.second, n);
606 } else if(stage && horseshoes[next.first][next.second] == ')') {
607 res = dfs(false, horseshoes, picked_cpy, count + 1, level - 1, next.first, next.second, n);
608 } else if(!stage && horseshoes[next.first][next.second] == ')') {
609 res = dfs(false, horseshoes, picked_cpy, count + 1, level - 1, next.first, next.second, n);
610 }
611 if(max < res) {
612 max = res;
613 }
614 }
615 }
616 return max;
617 }

725 void trie_node::insert(string str) {
726 if(str.length() == 0) {
727 return;
728 }
729 if(this->nexts[str[0] - '0'] == nullptr) {
730 this->nexts[str[0] - '0'] = new trie_node(str[0] - '0', this);
731 }
732 this->nexts[str[0] - '0']->insert(str.substr(1));
733 }
734
735 void trie_node::display() {
736 bool flag = true;
737 for(auto *next: this->nexts) {
738 if(next != nullptr) {
739 flag = false;
740 next->display();
741 }
742 }
743 if(flag) {
744 const auto *current = this;

1604 unsigned int Solution::count_reflect(direction d, unsigned int x, unsigned int y) {
1605 if(x == 0 || y == 0 || x == n - 1 || y == m - 1) {
1606 unsigned int count = 0;
1607 int current_x = x;
1608 int current_y = y;
1609 direction current_d = d;
1610 auto path = unordered_set<step, step_hash, step_equal>();
1611 while(0 <= current_x && current_x < n && 0 <= current_y && current_y < m) {
1612 auto s = step(current_d, current_x, current_y);
1613 if(!path.contains(s)) {
1614 path.insert(s);
1615 } else {
1616 return -1;
1617 }
1618
1619 const auto *record = get_record(d);
1620 if((*record)[x][y] != 0) {
1621 return count + (*record)[x][y];
1622 }
1623 current_d = reflect(current_d, mirrors[current_x][current_y]);
1624 count++;
1625 (*get_record(!current_d))[current_x][current_y] = count;
1626 switch(current_d) {
1627 case left: {
1628 current_y--;
1629 break;
1630 }
1631 case right: {
1632 current_y++;
1633 break;
1634 }
1635 case up: {
1636 current_x--;
1637 break;
1638 }
1639 case down: {
1640 current_x++;
1641 break;
1642 }
1643 }
1644 }
1645 return count;
1646 }
1647 return -1;
1648 }
1649
1650 unsigned int (*Solution::get_record(direction d))[1000][1000] {
1651 switch(d) {
1652 case left: {
1653 return &left_map;
1654 }
1655 case right: {
1656 return &right_map;
1657 }
1658 case up: {
1659 return &up_map;
1660 }
1661 case down: {
1662 return &down_map;
1663 }
1664 }
1665 return nullptr;
1666 }
1667
1668 direction reflect(direction d, char mirror) {
1669 switch(d) {
1670 case left: {
1671 if(mirror == '/') {
1672 return down;
1673 }
1674 if(mirror == '\\') {
1675 return up;
1676 }
1677 break;
1678 }
1679 case right: {
1680 if(mirror == '/') {
1681 return up;
1682 }
1683 if(mirror == '\\') {
1684 return down;
1685 }
1686 break;
1687 }
1688 case up: {
1689 if(mirror == '/') {
1690 return right;
1691 }
1692 if(mirror == '\\') {
1693 return left;
1694 }
1695 break;
1696 }
1697 case down: {
1698 if(mirror == '/') {
1699 return left;
1700 }
1701 if(mirror == '\\') {
1702 return right;
1703 }
1704 break;
1705 }
1706 }
1707 return {};
1708 }
1709
1710 direction operator!(const direction &d) {
1711 switch(d) {
1712 case left: {
1713 return right;
1714 }
1715 case right: {
1716 return left;
1717 }
1718 case up: {
1719 return down;
1720 }
1721 case down: {
1722 return up;
1723 }
1724 }
1725 return {};
1726 }
1727
1728 unsigned long step_hash::operator()(const step &s) const { return s.d * 1000 * 1000 + s.x * 1000 + s.y; }
1729
1730 bool step_equal::operator()(const step &s1, const step &s2) const { return s1.d == s2.d && s1.x == s2.x && s1.y == s2.y; }

2053 unsigned long long acwing4213::get_min(vector<char> ops, vector<unsigned long long> vec) {
2054 const char op = ops[0];
2055 if(vec.size() == 2) {
2056 if(op == '+') {
2057 return vec[0] + vec[1];
2058 }
2059 return vec[0] * vec[1];
2060 }
2061 const auto next_ops = vector(ops.begin() + 1, ops.end());
2062 unsigned long long minimum = 1000000000000;
2063 for(int i = 0; i < vec.size() - 1; i++) {
2064 for(int j = i + 1; j < vec.size(); j++) {
2065 unsigned long long new_num;
2066 if(op == '+') {
2067 new_num = vec[i] + vec[j];
2068 } else {
2069 new_num = vec[i] * vec[j];
2070 }
2071 auto new_vec = vector<unsigned long long>();
2072 new_vec.push_back(new_num);
2073 for(int k = 0; k < vec.size(); k++) {
2074 if(k != i && k != j) {
2075 new_vec.push_back(vec[k]);
2076 }
2077 }
2078 const auto ret = get_min(next_ops, new_vec);
2079 if(minimum > ret) {
2080 minimum = ret;
2081 }
2082 }
2083 }
2084 return minimum;

4758 void acwing818::sort(int *a, int l, int r) {
4759 if(l == r) {
4760 return;
4761 }
4762 if(l + 1 == r) {
4763 if(a[l] < a[r]) {
4764 return;
4765 }
4766 const int tmp = a[l];
4767 a[l] = a[r];
4768 a[r] = tmp;
4769 }
4770 const int m = a[(l + r) / 2];
4771 deque<int> dq;
4772 int cursor = l;
4773 dq.push_back(m);
4774 for(int i = l; i <= r; i++) {
4775 if(i != (l + r) / 2) {
4776 if(a[i] <= m) {
4777 dq.push_front(a[i]);
4778 cursor++;
4779 } else {
4780 dq.push_back(a[i]);
4781 }
4782 }
4783 }
4784 for(int i = l; i <= r; i++) {
4785 a[i] = dq[i - l];
4786 }
4787 if(l <= cursor - 1) {
4788 sort(a, l, cursor - 1);
4789 }
4790 if(r >= cursor + 1) {
4791 sort(a, cursor + 1, r);
4792 }
4793 }

6299 if(l >= r) {
6300 return;
6301 }
6302 const int x = vec[l + r >> 1];
6303 int lp = l - 1;

6305 while(lp < rp) {
6306 while(vec[++lp] < x) {}

6308 if(lp < rp) {

6310 }

6313 qs(vec, rp + 1, r);

6505 this->nexts[str[start]] = new TrieNode(str[start]);
6506 }

6508 this->nexts[str[start]]->origin.insert(origin);
